OL,3,CWindfall tax on banks could recoup QE
OL,4,Closses and raise #8bn a year, IPPR says
OL,6,FThe think tank argues the UK is an
OL,7,Finternational outlier in having its
OL,8,FTreasury pay for central Bank losses
OL,9,Fon its bond-buying quantitative easing
OL,10,F(QE) programme.
OL,12,FAfter a period of making profits on
OL,13,Fthis programme, the Bank of England is
OL,14,Ffacing record losses, estimated to
OL,15,Fcost the taxpayer #22 billion a year,
OL,16,Fas interest rates have risen since
OL,17,F2021, it warned.
