OL,3,CWindfall tax on banks could recoup QE
OL,4,Closses and raise #8bn a year, IPPR says
OL,6,FThis money is then partly being
OL,7,Ffunnelled to bank shareholders due to
OL,8,Fa "flawed" policy design, boosting
OL,9,Fprofits while millions across Britain
OL,10,Fcontinue to face cost-of-living
OL,11,Fpressures, the report says.
OL,13,FIt recommends the Treasury introduce a
OL,14,F"QE reserves income levy", similar to
OL,15,Fthe 2.5% deposit tax imposed on banks
OL,16,Funder Margaret Thatcher in 1981, to
OL,17,Frebalance the existing set-up.
