OL,3,CWindfall tax on banks could recoup QE
OL,4,Closses and raise #8bn a year, IPPR says
OL,6,FUnder the proposals, the receipts from
OL,7,Fthe banks levy would be used to
OL,8,Fsupport "households and growth" and
OL,9,Fwould fall to zero once all QE-related
OL,10,Fgilts are off the Bank of England's
OL,11,Fbalance sheet, or when the bank rate
OL,12,Freaches 2%, meaning the tax would be
OL,13,Ftemporary.
OL,15,FGiven the "targeted" nature of the
OL,16,Ftax, it should only have a "small
OL,17,Fimpact, if any" on UK banks'
OL,18,Fcompetitiveness and smaller banks
OL,19,Fshould be exempted from the measure,
OL,20,Fthe think tank said.
